Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--text--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.80,0:00:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙躲到哪裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.78,0:00:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓋伊烏斯大人  從海流上考慮的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.14,0:00:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是朝島的西南方向去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.21,0:00:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.38,0:00:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您看如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.34,0:00:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去隆狄尼姆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.06,0:00:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隆狄尼姆嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.85,0:00:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  有點事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.36,0:00:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.69,0:00:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  大戰前要那個啥來著的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.54,0:00:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微休息一下吧  也這樣通知士兵們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.95,0:00:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.07,0:01:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.91,0:01:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓城堡復活  我們已經解除了「生命之門」的堅固結界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.97,0:01:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被他們發現是早晚的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.99,0:01:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要開戰的話  一切都還太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.96,0:01:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖這麼說  但他們不會等我們擺好陣勢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.25,0:01:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.66,0:01:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武器也還不夠充足
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.69,0:01:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有必要統整好我們的軍勢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.16,0:01:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.21,0:03:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.17,0:03:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點快點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.59,0:03:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去玩了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.53,0:03:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.68,0:03:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南瓜瓜瓜  南瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.44,0:03:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這麼多  晚飯應該夠吃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.36,0:03:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.34,0:03:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉姆莉斯小姐  艾露敏小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.63,0:04:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的晚飯做蓋爾火鍋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.42,0:04:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～  又是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.52,0:04:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.80,0:04:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…蓋爾火鍋真是不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.73,0:04:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火鍋嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.82,0:04:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  是火鍋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.37,0:04:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祈禱不是螃蟹火鍋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.32,0:04:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祈禱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.38,0:04:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在這兒偷懶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.55,0:04:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷懶？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.07,0:04:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易回到我闊別已久的城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.85,0:04:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我懷念一下故鄉不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.42,0:04:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不讓人民挨餓  族長帶頭打獵  這是蓋爾族的規定…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.09,0:04:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是  那個我已經聽厭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.45,0:04:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管那麼多  給我過來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別扯啊  喂  快放手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.88,0:05:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  全部抓起來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.68,0:05:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.02,0:05:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太安靜了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來有其他人在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.36,0:05:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  這裡是其他部族的狩獵區
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.86,0:05:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能擅自闖入
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.71,0:05:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～  真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.80,0:05:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找別的狩獵區吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小摩真是的  喝太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.45,0:06:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種情況怎麼能不喝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.08,0:06:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有肉的蓋爾火鍋…根本算不上蓋爾火鍋！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有活力真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.06,0:06:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.41,0:06:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猴子？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.10,0:06:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰…誰是猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.72,0:06:31.83,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,註：猴子的日文發音就是撒魯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.72,0:06:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是阿爾撒魯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪你這第一戰士工作不積極
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.01,0:06:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們才落到連肉都吃不上的這步田地啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.62,0:06:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小摩別這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.03,0:06:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別老「摩」「摩」地叫我了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是牛！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.33,0:06:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猴子  我第二戰士摩爾嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.09,0:06:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為第一戰士的寶座  向你提出決鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.45,0:06:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.98,0:06:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.03,0:07:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆大人  不做點什麼的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.76,0:07:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩位  這是族長命令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.58,0:07:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場決鬥我允許了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.84,0:07:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  不要這種時候才擺出族長的架子…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猴子～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.21,0:07:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.51,0:07:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別跑  猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.52,0:07:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.98,0:07:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿起劍來和我決鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.68,0:07:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  阿隆  快想想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.25,0:07:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要有點第一戰士的氣概  自己解決吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.76,0:07:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧伽姆大人快想想辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.08,0:07:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  老是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好哦  摩爾嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.40,0:07:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差一口氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.79,0:07:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.67,0:07:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧伽姆  這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.51,0:07:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是豎琴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.05,0:07:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…這真是稀奇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.14,0:08:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾撒魯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.41,0:08:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀呀  不認識的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.20,0:08:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在舉行宴會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.90,0:08:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.60,0:08:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱愛歌唱和音樂的流浪的吟遊詩人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.72,0:08:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字是塔列辛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.84,0:08:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  吟遊詩人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真是稀奇  居然能在這附近遇上吟遊詩人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽一聽我這來自大陸的歌聲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要讓宴會氣氛熱烈起來  再合適不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.13,0:08:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀哦呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.96,0:09:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算禮貌一點說  今天的收穫也不算豐盛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有果物的火鍋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.48,0:09:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  讓我用歌聲為你們打氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.88,0:09:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心  代價只要把你們採來的蘑菇分一點給我就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.74,0:10:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不錯的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.65,0:10:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  受您誇獎真是光榮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.51,0:10:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  你們難道說是…蓋爾族嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.94,0:10:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是帝國那邊的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.68,0:10:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.56,0:10:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼是打算把我們的事告訴帝國嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.18,0:10:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是個不錯的想法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.10,0:10:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀不好  待太久了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.22,0:10:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.85,0:11:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  告訴你們一件事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.59,0:11:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這附近是被稱為布利岡第斯族的山賊的地盤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.33,0:11:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來已經明白了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.96,0:11:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我就在此告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.22,0:11:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔列辛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.61,0:11:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝你給大家帶來了快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定還有機會唱給你們聽的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.42,0:11:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  蓋伊烏斯他來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.88,0:12:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  似乎是追著那些蠻族來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.15,0:12:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.85,0:12:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然  只要他們行動起來  錢就會滾滾而來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.27,0:12:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再讓我賺上一筆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隆狄尼姆嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.80,0:12:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論什麼時候來都是個老舊的城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.39,0:12:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隆狄尼姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.68,0:12:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  從這裡向南
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.08,0:12:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是阿魯比昂島最大的貿易都市  屬於神聖帝國
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.63,0:12:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔  一口氣攻進敵人的據點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.47,0:12:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近狩獵一點都不夠爽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.94,0:12:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心裡癢癢的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:12:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  別急
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.96,0:13:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  害怕了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.40,0:13:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  魔王怎麼會害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.66,0:13:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要怎麼做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.25,0:13:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是  總之先去觀光吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.65,0:13:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  這城市真大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.87,0:13:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是隆狄尼姆  真是熱鬧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.79,0:13:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是酒場嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.60,0:13:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各種各樣的人聚在這裡  好像很有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.85,0:13:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿瓦隆城裡只有蓋爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼突然幹什麼啊  阿爾撒魯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.45,0:14:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨…笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.83,0:14:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我適可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.27,0:14:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥…哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.93,0:14:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.28,0:14:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在鬧市中大喊大叫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.77,0:14:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的身份暴露了該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.77,0:14:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.79,0:14:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那份精力就留到正式戰鬥再釋放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.59,0:14:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔  交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.75,0:14:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是精力旺盛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.46,0:14:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼觀光也到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.80,0:14:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.62,0:14:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.99,0:14:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  來自神聖帝國本土的物資全都經過這個城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.91,0:15:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運送到各個前線基地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.30,0:15:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  按照計劃行事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.97,0:15:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.72,0:15:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.90,0:15:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓋伊烏斯大人  差不多該去把那些傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.33,0:15:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  別心急
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.44,0:15:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓋伊烏斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.87,0:15:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼大一個城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我們不去迎接  對方也會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.58,0:15:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧…故意來我們的地盤這樣的行為
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.83,0:15:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不會做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.92,0:15:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.82,0:15:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的對手可是魔王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.57,0:15:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.39,0:15:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個「不可能」對我們來說正是好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.47,0:16:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.69,0:16:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫阿爾撒魯  乖乖丟下行李離開
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.67,0:16:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然就殺了你們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.05,0:16:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區一個蠻族能做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.99,0:16:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.71,0:16:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  諸位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.42,0:16:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.82,0:17:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.53,0:17:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.66,0:17:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.95,0:17:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.47,0:17:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.41,0:17:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩爾嘉  借你的弓箭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.88,0:17:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝國的手下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.91,0:18:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓋伊烏斯的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.33,0:18:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.70,0:18:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.58,0:18:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙子？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.71,0:18:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊也是沙子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.12,0:18:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中陷阱了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.44,0:18:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.19,0:18:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.58,0:18:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可沒時間喪氣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.02,0:18:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.56,0:18:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快會接到通報  趕過來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.76,0:18:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就只能反擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.21,0:18:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾撒魯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.14,0:18:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.08,0:18:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方的數量都沒弄清楚就打算反擊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.56,0:18:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們被耍了  怎麼能就這樣回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.66,0:18:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜下來！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.22,0:18:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算帶著那份懊悔和憤怒戰鬥  也無法獲得勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.18,0:18:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.36,0:19:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.36,0:19:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.68,0:19:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.59,0:19:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.64,0:19:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  挺能幹的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.27,0:20:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.14,0:20:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.16,0:20:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.61,0:20:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.68,0:20:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪  阿隆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.55,0:20:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.28,0:20:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆  去狩獵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.52,0:21:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點準備
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.86,0:21:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是螃蟹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.62,0:21:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小摩真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.97,0:21:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼快就出現了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.26,0:21:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像和螃蟹不一樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.24,0:21:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.87,0:21:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…人類？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.54,0:21:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧伽姆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.10,0:21:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是…


